Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present to market for sale or lease this brand new facility which is due for completion September 2021 (approximately).

This outstanding facility boasts a high truss tilt panel warehouse, 3 phase power, automatic gates, air conditioned offices and more.

This property is being offered for sale at $3,250,000 plus GST and for lease at an asking rental of $195,000 per annum plus outgoings and GST

This brand new development is a high truss tilt panel warehouse with an insulated metal deck roof and a concrete car park and driveway.  The offices will be carpeted with reverse cycle air conditioning, lighting and suspended ceilings.

- Garrison fencing
- Automatic sliding gates
- LED lighting to warehouse with skylights
- Disabled amenities with shower
- Kitchen facilities
- Security alarm system
- NDT for further NBN
- Landscaping
- Dual access
- Zoned General Industrial

BUILDING AREAS
Warehouse 1225sqm
Ground floor office 110sqm
First floor office 110sqm

This property will also be available for lease at a rental of $118,000 per annum plus outgoings and GST.
